{#- Live-data band — LOCKED grammar §2 row 5 (design lock 2026-07-07).
    C's dark editorial band: title + stamp, 4 stats with DELTA CONTEXT in the
    band's QUIET LABEL COLOR (--c-dark-sub; 8.84:1 on ink — rationale §7).
    Deliberately NO green/red valence palette (§4 migration rule: B's organ in
    editorial dress; valence color is a wave-2 data-viz spec decision INSIDE
    the locked system).

    DATA: while feed.marketStats is null (wave 2 wires the feed mirror,
    SQL-computed — plan §3a), the band renders SAMPLE-labeled figures. The
    caller may override via {% set band = {...} %} before including.

    ART. 15 NOTICE SLOT (round-2 grade finding 9, bound in §6): at Build the
    notice must name the ACTUAL period per stat surface — one "for the period
    shown" line over mixed periods is a labeled-sample liberty a live page may
    not take. The per-surface periods are therefore named IN the slot below.

    STUDIO-CREDIT LINE — the §4a bound copy, exact, do not paraphrase. -#}
{%- set band = band or {
  title: "The market, plainly read — July",
  stamp: "SAMPLE — at Build: computation timestamp",
  stats: [
    { num: "$412,500", lbl: "Median sale price",     delta: "▼ 1.8% vs June" },
    { num: "34",       lbl: "Median days on market", delta: "▲ 3 vs June" },
    { num: "1,284",    lbl: "Active listings",       delta: "▲ 37 this week" },
    { num: "3.1 mo",   lbl: "Supply",                delta: "as of this morning" }
  ],
  art15: "[Art. 15 notice slot — at Build names the actual period per surface: median price + DOM (trailing 90 days), active listings + supply (point-in-time at computation)]"
} -%}
<section class="databand" data-sec="databand" aria-label="Market snapshot">
  <div class="databand__in">
    <div class="databand__head">
      <h2>{{ band.title }}</h2>
      <p class="databand__stamp">{{ band.stamp }}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="databand__stats">
      {%- for s in band.stats %}
      <div class="stat">
        <p class="num">{{ s.num }}</p>
        <p class="lbl">{{ s.lbl }}</p>
        {%- if s.delta %}<p class="delta">{{ s.delta }}</p>{% endif %}
      </div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    <p class="databand__note">SAMPLE FIGURES &mdash; at Build these compute daily from the live Stellar MLS feed &middot; {{ band.art15 }}</p>
    <p class="databand__credit"><a href="/ai/">Computed and refreshed by Everlane&rsquo;s own studio automation &mdash; see how this site runs &rarr;</a></p>
  </div>
</section>
